byline.contributor: Erik Eckholm reported from Los Angeles, and Ashley Southall from New York.
byline.original: By ERIK ECKHOLM and ASHLEY SOUTHALL

abstract: Reality television star and former Olympic champion Bruce Jenner is involved in multicar accident in Malibu, Calif, that leaves one person dead and five injured; Jenner reportedly suffers no injuries.
lead_paragraph: The former Olympian was involved in a three-vehicle crash in Malibu that left one person dead and five injured. Mr. Jenner was not injured.

headline.main: Bruce Jenner Involved in Deadly Car Crash in Malibu
headline.print_headline: Jenner Involved in Deadly Car Crash in Malibu
